Full Description: StoryFile is changing the way people interact and communicate with each other and the world. Through user-led voice-activated technology  advanced AI and beyond  StoryFile provides a platform for an intimate and natural conversational video interactive experience. StoryFile is a content-driven technology company that allows individuals to preserve  share  and consume stories and experiences through its proprietary and innovative legacy capture system. StoryFile is reimagining storytelling by authentically preserving memories  moments  and beyond  in a meaningful way that empowers the storyteller and user. By preserving stories and history in a way that allows users to have authentic interactions  StoryFile is not only creating a new form of storytelling  but is also creating more sustainable bonds between people  everywhere. Creating a world where everyone  anywhere  anytime  can connect with those living or in the past is finally a reality with StoryFile.  This visual and interactive storytelling platform allows people to have a natural conversation across time and space. Just think – StoryFile gives your great-great grandchildren an opportunity to speak with you  learn from you  and get to know you in a way that was never possible before. The gift of storytelling – the gift of passing experiences to future generations – is priceless. StoryFile wants to ensure each and every person has such opportunity – from the Studio experience to the app  there is something for everyone! Here’s how it works: An individual is filmed (or films themselves) answering questions about their life  which are then processed and stored on the StoryFile platform. Users can then have a real life-like conversation with the filmed-version of the individual on the web or mobile application – anytime  anywhere. StoryFile’s platform promotes user-led education and curiosity  providing an opportunity for users to directly engage with the interviewee. StoryFile captures the interviewee’s legacy in a unique way by empowering the interviewee to pass on their values  struggles  life lessons  morals  decisions and more  while inspiring future generations. About The StoryFile Experience: The StoryFile experience is intimate  personal and truly unique. StoryFile has created a warm and comfortable studio space for the interviewee to share his/her life lessons  personal memories  struggles  triumphs  joys  milestones  and more. The most important thing about you is your story  so it’s the most important story to tell. StoryFile’s team takes the time to get to know you  and works with you and your family to craft and facilitate the telling of that story  as it is the most important gift to future generations you will ever give. StoryFile’s studio is equipped with cutting edge technology that produces 3D assets as well as Hi-Fidelity 2D images. This is how the magic is made.

In the digital age  humans cannot physically read and digest every bit of information relevant to a given decision. In addition  almost every organization has what is called 'dark' or 'siloed' data – valuable data that is not being used  or that organizations don’t know they have at their disposal. It is estimated that as much as 90% of the data within a given organization is dark or siloed. As a result  pharmaceutical companies are making important decisions with incomplete information. ENTER TRIALS.AI - we are on a mission to get effective treatments to patients faster by using artificial intelligence to optimize clinical trial designs for speed and success. Full Description: SimpleMachines (SMI) has created a Software-Defined Compute platform that is future-proofed against the growing needs of artificial intelligence  virtual reality  machine learning  robotics  and big data. Traditional computer systems (CPUs) were designed to be easily programmable  which allowed technology to permeate every facet of daily life. But the software those systems ran only got faster as a result of the doubling of performance every 2 years (Moore’s Law)  which has recently come to an end. Software has gotten more complex and data sets are growing exponentially  creating the need for a new chip platform. Recently  the industry has resorted to building single purpose systems (ASICs) that are impossible to reprogram. These hardware-only (chip) solutions are incredibly expensive  take years to develop and deploy (3+ years)  and run the risk of being obsolete by the time they are ready  making them poor investments for the rapidly changing software and environments they are meant to enable. SimpleMachines’s solution is a radically new software-centric approach to the problem that deploys a programmable platform with a breakthrough software stack that enables the programmer to easily optimize the hardware on the fly and get the performance of custom silicon with a platform that supports hundreds of different use cases.
Industries: Artificial Intelligence  Machine Learning  Semiconductor
Description: SimpleMachines has created a Software-Defined Compute Platform that is future-proofed for AI  ML VR  robotics  and big data.

Full Description: DB Networks innovates artificial intelligence based database security products. Their customers include the world’s largest financial institutions  healthcare providers  manufacturers  and governments. DB Networks non-intrusively discovers all databases  tables being accessed  and the applications accessing the databases. Machine learning is used to immediately and accurately identify compromised credentials and database attacks. Customers gain insights and a situational awareness of IT infrastructure including four primary benefits:    * Non-intrusively and continuously discovering all databases    * Deep analysis into database activity    * Pinpoint insider threats    * Artificial intelligence identifies insider threatsDB Networks continuous database infrastructure monitoring "shines a light" on what's really going on in your infrastructure. For example  undocumented and unmanaged databases may contain highly sensitive information and offer cyber attackers an enormously large attack surface. DB Networks non-intrusively discovers all databases and the interactions of users and applications to their connected databases. Advanced Persistent Threats (APTs) operating inside the core network introduce new  or alter user/application interactions. DB Networks maps all of these application interactions to rapidly identify APTs. Continuous monitoring the core network also identifies policy violations such as restricted databases being exposed to unrestricted network segments.DB Networks’ unique approach to intelligent database security utilizes machine learning and behavioral analysis to automatically create models of each applications proper interactions with their connected databases. These models are used to immediately and accurately identify database attacks. With no signature files to deal with or endless false positives to chase down operational support of DB Networks products becomes trivial.DB Networks is a privately held company headquartered in San Diego  California.

Full Description: Faceter is a video surveillance and security platform based on artificial vision technology and an approach that involves analyzing the chain of events happening in the frame and responding to them. We call it "the event-based security model".Most of the video surveillance software products currently available on the market operate in two categories: time of recording and source. This means a user can only see what was recorded at a particular time frame on each of the installed cameras.Faceter makes video surveillance systems much more capable by adding face recognition technology. Faceter can build a list of office workers  family members  restaurant patrons; generate a report on who was detected and when  in the cameras' scope; find each occurrence of a specific person at a specific location and retrieve specific records from the archive.Faceter can be taught to respond to certain events. For example  the system can send SMS to parents when their child arrives from school  and transmit information to integrated systems via available APIs. It could be a smart house management platform that will send a command to warm up food in the microwave. In the next two years we will make Faceter support protocols for several leading smart house platforms and standard callback APIs.When integrated with urban services  Faceter can be configured to perform specific actions  such as sending alerts to 911 if there are signs of violence or incipient crime.

Full Description: With Lodestar you can annotate video far faster than with any other available tools. Lodestar lets you drag and drop hours of video and start annotating right away. It continuously trains a custom AI as you label. The AI automatically predicts labels  greatly speeding up the work. As the AI gets more accurate  so do the labels  so the annotation team can generate more labels faster than ever.The custom AI also drives our active learning system that automatically finds objects buried in hours of video and queues up the frames for the team to check. It adds the most helpful frames to the top of the queue  so the dataset gains the most valuable data first  and the model gets better faster.Finally  integrated dataset management and data science tools allow data scientists to run experiments and validate the dataset by training inference models in parallel with the labeling effort. No wasted time and money creating labels that aren't adding value to the dataset.Today  training a computer vision model can take months of multiple cycles of labeling  exporting  training a model  analyzing the results  and starting again to achieve success.Lodestar changes all that. Our advanced platform for labeling and training with native video support trains a model in real time and allows your teams to work in parallel. You’ll finish in weeks what used to take months.

Full Description: Lexibl is an emerging startup based in Los Angeles  California  that is focused on transforming the reading experience for the 2.4 billion people with dyslexia and ADHD. The company's mission is unlock the power of reading by providing software that allows everyone to read with ease focus  and power by creating accessible and engaging reading software.With approximately 2.4 billion people worldwide facing dyslexia and ADHD-related reading challenges  Lexibl recognizes the need to make digital documents work for everyone. Traditional digital documents often fail to accommodate the unique needs of individuals with dyslexia and ADHD  leading to feelings of overwhelm  constant re-reading  and reduced comprehension.Founder and CEO Lulu Waters  who personally manages dyslexia and ADHD  highlights the disparity between the digital revolution and the accessibility of digital documents for individuals with learning differences. To bridge this gap  Lexibl is developing software that breaks documents into manageable "micro-bursts" of reading and learning. Their patent pending software makes focusing on what you're reading easy with their reading panel. Drives comprehension and retention by allowing readers to engage with text int he way that works best for them. Additionally  their software provides personalized pauses to match readers' pacing and a learning board space for capturing insights to boost retention. Lexibl's vision extends beyond digital documents alone. The company aims to ensure that everyone can access and comprehend written digital content effortlessly. By alleviating reading overwhelm  Lexibl empowers people to read effortlessly   boost thier confidence  and overall performance in various aspects of life.The importance of addressing reading overwhelm  a term coined by Lexibl after interviewing adults ages 18 - 65 (with and without dyslexia and ADHD) to describe the experience individuals with dyslexia and ADHD face when trying to process large amounts of text. Through their revolutionary approach  Lexibl aims to provide effective tools that help individuals overcome reading challenges and facilitate a more enjoyable and accessible reading experience.By focusing on the specific needs of individuals with dyslexia and ADHD  Lexibl is poised to make a significant impact in the AI & Ed-tech spaces  fostering inclusivity and empowering individuals to thrive in their educational and professional pursuits.
Industries: Artificial Intelligence  E-Learning  EdTech  Education  Machine Learning  Software
Description: Advanced AI Solutions for Dyslexia and ADHD: Lexibl Redefines Reading

Full Description: Coral is a human-centric robotics company  designing robots for people to enhance their everyday lives. We believe that purpose-driven robots empower all people to achieve more.Robots have always been one of the greatest dreams and fears of people. We marvel at their capabilities  yet are terrified of what they can become. We want them to be intelligent  yet are constantly disappointed. We saw this paradox and thought what can we do differently?Using our backgrounds in engineering and design  we saw that we can use a thoughtful and people-first approach to making robots. Robots should work with people rather than do things only on their own. This relationship between person and robot should be one that’s constructive.When we were looking at where to call Coral home  it was important to us that it be a place filled with creativity  energy  and next to the ocean. We wanted to be in a place where we can foster talent and spark innovation. We wanted to be in a place where we can be reminded of the values of our brand. More importantly  we wanted to build a community of people who use design and robotics to empower people. That’s why Los Angeles is our home.We think robotics is an innovative and exciting space. We see a future with an ecosystem of robots that work together to help people in their daily lives. It’s important for us that we need to use thoughtful design to help get us to that future now.

Full Description: ViridisChem is a software company that has built the world’s largest toxicity database  and is developing SaaS  AI platform for toxicity evaluation of products and ingredients. Increasingly strict global regulations  litigation risks  and industry-wide push for cost reduction has created an urgent need for toxicity evaluations of not just the end-products  but also the starting materials. By screening out toxic drug targets  avoiding the use of toxic raw material  pharma and biochem companies can avoid many months of wasted R&D time  minimize the toxic waste generation  and avoid costly late-stage manufacturing changes. End result: less time and money needed to bring drug to market.For consumer sectors  by minimizing the use of toxic raw materials and formulations  they can minimize the risk of late-stage manufacturing changes  and increase govt. compliance  and brand recognition.What do we offer?:1)	Toxicity of less than 0.1% of chemicals is known. Scientists rely on material data-sheets  but 80% of these are either inaccurate or incomplete. We offer toxicity evaluation of all chemicals  including new molecules2)	Companies are having difficulty in keeping track of worldwide frequently changing government regulations and chemical threshold. We provide up-to-date compliance and chemical threshold information3)	Within consumer industries  suppliers don’t disclose formulation ingredients (their IP)  and they cannot accurately predict toxicity of their formulations  because the models that take into account the % composition of chemicals  and their interactions within mixtures don’t exist.  We are building such models using machine-learning algorithms ensuring increasing accuracy. By offering accurate toxicity related information throughout R&D  ViridisChem will lead the standardization of toxicity evaluation across all industriesOur Solution:We have built the most comprehensive toxicity database with over 90 million chemicals and 2.4 billion properties  curated using AI techniques  and are offering through yearly subscription  an AI powered SaaS software platform that provides toxicity evaluation (related to ecological  health and safety) of any chemical  even the new molecules  identifies local  regional  and per country regulatory issues and established thresholds related to the chemical use  allowing scientists to eliminate high-risk drug candidates. And minimize the use of toxic raw material.This is the Industry-first off-the-shelf toxicity evaluation product offering real-time toxicity evaluation of any chemical  even the new molecules. This much needed solution is proving to be so powerful  that ViridisChem received recognition by the United Nations Environment Program (UNEP) for offering solutions that will most benefit sustainability.
Industries: Artificial Intelligence  Biotechnology  Life Science  Machine Learning  Medical
Description: SaaS  AI powered software platform offering toxicity evaluation of any chemical  formulations/mixtures  and development processes.

Full Description: Coursa Retail: Achieving parity between online and offline shopper behavior data. High-accuracy in-store shopper path and behavior insights with no store infrastructure.What if there was a new  innovative approach to track in-store shopper behavior that delivers consistent in-aisle shopper position accuracy to 1.5 meters and addresses the scalability challenge by eliminating the need for any in-store systems or technology? Solving both of these challenges (accuracy and scalability) is possible today using motion sensing technology that is already available in most shopper smartphones. Accuracy and scalability are the driving factors behind the creation of Coursa RetailCoursa Retail helps retailers  brands and digital ad platforms to accurately measure or execute the following:Improved offline attribution: When a shopper views a digital mobile ad on their smartphone  does it lead to the shopper visiting the shelf in-store where that product is located.	In-store missed conversions: Measure all product categories that a shopper visits in-store. Highlight which category visits do not lead to a purchase (missed conversions). Enables retailers and brands to retarget these shoppers with incentives to purchase these products on their next visit to the store.	Personalization: Build detailed profiles of in-store shopper behavior based on the ability to record a shopper’s entire walking path and dwell points across all store visits.Coursa’s mobile SDK and SaaS platform uses smartphone motion sensors to capture every step  turn  dwell point  and product engagement shoppers make inside physical stores with meter-level accuracy. In-aisle  Coursa determines which shelf and bay the shopper is facing  which product category they look at  and how long they remain engaged.The Coursa Retail team is headquartered in San Jose  California

Full Description: Prophyles is reinventing Contact Management by pioneering a new category coined as Contacts-as-a-Service (CaaS).  Prophyles is solving the lingering problems in contact management related to data integrity  accuracy  synchronization  up-to-date  and privacy.  All current vendors  from low-end address books to high-end CRMs  use a centralized database which causes silos which are the main source of the problems.  Prophyles took a unique and contrarian approach by using a decentralized and distributed database in a peer-to-peer network in which profiles are connected using "Smart Contracts" in a blockchain - which is the core of our patent.Prophyles provides your entire digital footprint and those of your contacts  without ever compromising your or their privacy  and without ever being outdated since all Personal Information is constantly updated from the cloud onto your or their device  just like updates of mobile apps. Prophyles offers you the most comprehensive and protected profile; reduces the probability of identity theft; connects you easily and safely with others through customizable digital cards that represent your different personas which prevent hackers  spammers  or even online predators from preying on your children; leverages your social network by capitalizing on the strength of your weak ties to get you qualified referrals; gets the latest scoop from social media about your contacts; finds people near you; records your daily events in a personalized diary; organizes your ideas in a customized journal; generates flavors of your resumes that are fed to job boards; completes online forms through AI-empowered APIs for you so that you don’t have to  etc. In short  Prophyles is your digital footprint in a truly connected and more secured new online world.
